msgstr "Utilizați numele de utilizator ca nume comun"

msgid "VPN"
msgstr "VPN"

msgid ""
"When you have more than one IP address (e.g. multiple interfaces, or "
"secondary IP addresses), and do not use --local to force binding to one "
